## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React Native with Expo SDK 52
- **Language**: TypeScript 5
- **Navigation**: Expo Router (file-based routing)
- **Build**: EAS Build & Submit
- **Testing**: Jest + React Native Testing Library

## Prerequisites

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) 18+
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) 9+
- [Expo Go](https://expo.dev/client) app (for development) or
- Xcode (for iOS development)
- Android Studio (for Android development)

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
make install

# Start development server
make start

# Scan QR code with Expo Go app or run on simulator
make ios # iOS Simulator
make android # Android Emulator
```

## Development

### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `make start` | Start Expo development server |
| `make ios` | Run on iOS Simulator |
| `make android` | Run on Android Emulator |
| `make web` | Run in web browser |
| `make test` | Run tests |
| `make lint` | Lint code |
| `make typecheck` | TypeScript type check |

